{"tid":1820580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"正因為對待愛情認真 所以先搵SP","createTime":"2020-01-11T14:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T15:22:24.000Z","uid":209657,"like":48,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"4150e11d07d396c71b4671f5529b47f6007ee110","tid":1820580,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"愛情的確令到人有幸福既感覺<br />\n但當遇到唔順境就好麻煩<br />\n要磨合 要忍耐 要猜忌 要原諒<br />\n無時無刻控制住你既思緒<br />\n重視既人反而傷得更深<br />\n<br />\n甚至有啲人只係玩玩下<br />\n口講愛你 實際上只係你就手<br />\n遇到條件更好 或者厭倦左<br />\n就會搵個理由踢開你<br />\n<br />\nSP唔需要心靈上既契合<br />\n唔需要被約束 唔需要太在意<br />\n只要好似朋友一樣交流就可以<br />\n需要既時候約下佢出黎<br />\n可以保留自己既個人空間<br />\n想去邊都得 唔洗成日痴住<br />\n大家各取所需 互相取暖<br />\n<br />\n正因為對待愛情認真 <br />\n所以先唔輕易開始 <br />\n免得互相傷害"},{"pid":"e1602aca43ca27e8446a799e76f761fd5d5bb848","tid":1820580,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"明既 commitment issue"},{"pid":"5ca495db7355460b777180e6ae732bf9a12d3edf","tid":1820580,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"想切磋了"},{"pid":"12fdbbb76dc11c484b48f257128c9b2d613d4c66","tid":1820580,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"有點認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d933e06d498960e0d1506c224aba1f9ba9aeea","tid":1820580,"uid":170176,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"但SP都有機會會沉船啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果對感情認真 應該會專一地中意一個人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd7a8f65b0b2225d66949bbf91f9ee9a3b55bf6","tid":1820580,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"你作新詩？"},{"pid":"8aba6363695e77ba4c9d0e81f74276d182246cd2","tid":1820580,"uid":1691